text: "New York Minute" is a 1989 song by Don Henley. It was taken from his album The End of the Innocence. It went to number 48 in the United States in 1990. It has been associated with the September 11 attacks in New York. == References == Category:1989 songs Category:1980s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Don Henley songs Category:Rock songs
